    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of pride-of-ownership and practical use. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous gloss, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather seats are supple, with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the navigation system\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is turn-key ready. It has a comprehensive service history, with a recent oil service and a multi-point inspection just completed. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the tires provide excellent grip with plenty of life remaining. If you are looking for a reliable, well-documented car that looks as good as it performs, this is the one.",
